name: Primary Cloud (Yellow)
description:
Part 1 of 3 part series. In which one cloud is placed in a primary color with stick figures representing subconscious thoughts(and one primary color), lines and some basic geometry(for the third primary color).This is the yellow cloud. The goal of these works is to use minimal color, but with as much expression as possible while working with as little of the canvas as possible, to create something balanced and big.

4000px x 4000px
